    "This is in fact the simplest example of non-invertible symmetry fractionalization.",
    "It is furnished by a surface operator O 2 in a d-dimensional QFT T carrying a is the identity line on O 2 and D (-) 1 generates a 2 localized 0-form symmetry of O 2: D (-) 1 ⊗ D (-) 1 = D (id) 1.",
